OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FParanoid schizophrenic Valdo Calocane
OL,7,Fwas discharged from mental health
OL,8,Fservices to his GP just months before
OL,9,Fhe killed three people in Nottingham
OL,10,Fbecause healthcare workers could not
OL,11,Ffind him, an inquiry has heard.
OL,13,FFormer mechanical engineering student
OL,14,FCalocane had been under the care of
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust for two years, during
OL,17,Fwhich time a consultant psychiatrist
OL,18,Fwarned that he would end up killing
OL,19,Fsomeone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FIn September 2022, Calocane was
OL,7,Fdischarged by the trust's Early
OL,8,FIntervention in Psychosis (EIP)
OL,9,Fservice because he failed to turn up
OL,10,Ffor appointments or make contact with
OL,11,Fthe team.
OL,13,FMonths later, he stabbed to death
OL,14,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,15,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, in Ilkeston
OL,16,FRoad in Nottingham, and Ian Coates,
OL,17,F65, in the early hours of June 13
OL,18,F2023, before he tried to murder three
OL,19,Fmore people with a stolen van in the
OL,20,Fcity centre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FEmma Robinson, who was a team leader
OL,7,Fat the trust told the inquiry, which
OL,8,Fis looking into events leading up to
OL,9,Fthe attacks, on Tuesday, that
OL,10,FCalocane's care co-ordinator, Gary
OL,11,FCarter, had attended his address, made
OL,12,Fcalls to him, and sent a letter that
OL,13,Fwent unanswered.
OL,15,F"We had no holding powers"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FTim Moloney KC, who represents the
OL,7,Ffamilies of Mr Webber, Ms O'Malley-
OL,8,FKumar and Mr Coates, asked, "When you
OL,9,Fdischarged, did you think about the
OL,10,Frisk to the public from this man, who
OL,11,FEIP would not visit alone, would not
OL,12,Fvisit at home unless absolutely
OL,13,Fnecessary?
OL,15,F"Did you consider the risks to the
OL,16,Fpublic from that man?"
OL,26,@pD@]OUwD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FShe replied, "We did consider that,
OL,7,Fbut we felt that within the time of
OL,8,Fdecision, we had no holding powers, we
OL,9,Fcouldn't work with him, we couldn't
OL,10,Ffind him at this point. We just
OL,11,Fcouldn't find him to work with him."
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard that Calocane's last
OL,14,Fengagement with the EIP team had been
OL,15,Fby phone on July 16, when he lied
OL,16,Fabout being abroad.
OL,18,FMr Moloney asked, "Had you lost him?"
OL,19,Fto which Ms Robinson replied, "Yes."
OL,26,@nD@NOUsD@dO]zD@SOUzD@eO]{D@_OU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe lawyer asked, "Is that primarily
OL,7,Fwhy you discharged him?"
OL,9,FMs Robinson said, "Yes, because we
OL,10,Fcouldn't find him to treat him or
OL,11,Fengage him."
OL,13,FMr Moloney said that by discharging
OL,14,FCalocane to his GP, the trust "left
OL,15,Fhim to the general public to deal
OL,16,Fwith".
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@XO]qD@SOUsD@LO]vD@_OUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FMs Robinson said, "I wouldn't say the
OL,7,Fgeneral public to deal with. It's not
OL,8,Funcommon for us to discharge non-
OL,9,Fengaging patients, unfortunately, at
OL,10,Fthat time. I think things are very
OL,11,Fdifferent now."
OL,13,FIn a statement written by Ms Robinson
OL,14,Fexplaining her rationale for
OL,15,Fdischarging Calocane, she said:
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,F"It's dire for me to think this now,
OL,7,Fbut I used to think sometimes is it
OL,8,Fworse to have somebody open on
OL,9,Fcaseloads that you're not engaging
OL,10,Fwith? Should we be discharging them
OL,11,Finstead?
OL,13,F"What does it look like if something
OL,14,Fhappens and we've got this person open
OL,15,Fto us and we haven't seen him for
OL,16,Fmonths and months and months?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FAsked to explain this statement by
OL,7,Fcounsel to the inquiry, Craig Carr, Ms
OL,8,FRobinson said, "I suppose, from
OL,9,Fprevious experience, I'm worried about
OL,10,Fhow that's looked ` that we've got
OL,11,Fsomebody that's open to us, and
OL,12,Fperhaps we've not been able to treat
OL,13,Fthem for nine months, or find them.
OL,15,F"So sometimes the decision's better to
OL,16,Fdischarge back to the GP."
OL,18,FMr Carr said it could be interpreted
OL,19,Fthat Ms Robinson was suggesting that
OL,20,Fit is better to get someone "off the
OL,21,Fbooks" if they cannot be found.
OL,26,@pD@POUwD@AOUxD@ZO]|D@]OU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe witness said, "It feels safer to
OL,7,Fhave somebody discharged back to the
OL,8,Fqueue of the GP, than open to a
OL,9,Fsecondary service when we can't engage
OL,10,Fthem, or we can't do anything for
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FChairwoman Deborah Taylor said
OL,14,FCalocane's GP was "effectively sent
OL,15,Fvery little information" after his
OL,16,Fdischarge.
OL,18,FMs Robinson said, "I accept that."
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@FO]vD@SOUwD@XO]zD@SOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
