PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778186662
OL,3,CTriple killer discharged because NHS
OL,4,Ctrust could not find him, inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe witness also told the inquiry that
OL,7,Fthe trust did not tell Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice that Calocane had been
OL,9,Fdischarged from its services.
OL,11,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
